Cardiology patient page. Neurodevelopmental outcomes in congenital heart 
disease.

Rollins CK(1), Newburger JW(2).

Author information:
(1)From the Departments of Neurology (C.K.R.) and Cardiology (J.W.N.), Boston 
Children's Hospital, and the Departments of Neurology (C.K.R.) and Pediatrics 
(J.W.N.), Harvard Medical School, Boston, MA. 
